results.description:
We were staying across the road from a temple in Varkala during festival season. Looking out the window early one morning I noticed some elephants being led into the temple. I grabbed the camera was able to get photos that covered their entire outing for the day - everything from a morning bath to parading through the local streets and then back to the temple.

This is morning preparation.
